            <p>All bids placed on this platform are legally binding. By placing a bid you agree to:</p>
            <ul class="static-list">
                <li>Pay the full bid amount if you are the winning bidder</li>
                <li>Not retract a bid once it has been placed</li>
                <li>Only bid on properties you genuinely intend to purchase</li>
                <li>Ensure all bids exceed the current highest bid</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="static-section">
            <h2>3. Property Listings</h2>
